OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,FITV News reporter Kathy Wardle speaks
OL,7,Fto businesses and residents affected
OL,8,Fby water supply issues in Cornwall
OL,10,FHomes and businesses in West Cornwall
OL,11,Fhave told ITV News they have been left
OL,12,F"frustrated" after experiencing
OL,13,F"repeated failures" with their water
OL,14,Fsupply.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,FResidents and businesses across
OL,7,FNancledra, Carbis Bay, Halsetown,
OL,8,FCripplesease, Towednack and
OL,9,Fsurrounding areas have reported more
OL,10,Fthan 30 incidents since January
OL,11,Faccording to Andrew George, Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrat MP for West Cornwall and the
OL,13,FIsles of Scilly.
OL,15,FSouth West Water has apologised for
OL,16,Fthe disruption caused to residents and
OL,17,Fbusinesses, saying "increased seasonal
OL,18,Fdemand is putting pressure" on the
OL,19,Fnetwork.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,FBecky Osbourne, owner of Polmanter
OL,7,FHoliday Park in St Ives, said: ''Over
OL,8,Fthe bank holiday weekend, we noticed a
OL,9,Fdrop in our water pressure early on
OL,10,FSunday morning.
OL,12,F"And a spell after that, the water
OL,13,Fstopped entirely and which meant that
OL,14,Fwe weren't able to operate our showers
OL,15,Facross the site at a peak time in the
OL,16,Fmorning when everybody wants to get
OL,17,Fup, have a shower and get ready for
OL,18,Ftheir day."
OL,20,FMs Osbourne says they pay more than
OL,21,F#30,000 a year for water supply.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,F"Our guests expect in return that when
OL,7,Fthey come to a five-star site like
OL,8,Fthis, they're going to get clean,
OL,9,Fplentiful hot showers", she added.
OL,11,FAlthough the most recent situation has
OL,12,Fnow been addressed, Ms Osbourne says
OL,13,Fshe has been flagging a supply issue
OL,14,F"well in advance" to MPs and local
OL,15,Fcouncillors.
OL,17,FThe site was impacted by intermittent
OL,18,Fsupply issues during Storm Goretti.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,F"We were really disappointed that it
OL,7,Fwas entirely predictable and the
OL,8,Fmeasures that have now been put in
OL,9,Fshould have been implemented much
OL,10,Fearlier", Ms Osbourne said.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Darren Biggs, Landlord of
OL,13,FThe Engine Inn in Penzance, said his
OL,14,Fbusiness lost a lot of trade at the
OL,15,Fweekend, which hits them hard as a
OL,16,Fseasonal business.
OL,18,FOver the bank holiday, temperatures
OL,19,Freached record levels for May. He
OL,20,Festimates the business has lost around
OL,21,F#4,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,FHe told ITV News that the business had
OL,7,Fto hire portable toilets as a result
OL,8,Fof the issues.
OL,10,F"It's just not acceptable when we're
OL,11,Fstruggling as a business, especially
OL,12,Fin the climate we're in, being in
OL,13,Fhospitality and seasonal", he said.
OL,15,F"We felt we'd get a bit more support
OL,16,Ffrom (South West Water), but
OL,17,Funfortunately we didn't."
OL,19,FSpeaking to ITV News, Andrew George MP
OL,20,Fsaid issues have been going on since
OL,21,Fthe start of the year.
OL,26,@yD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,F"There have been vulnerable households
OL,7,Fleft without any water supply and in
OL,8,Fthe current heatwave, that's
OL,9,Funacceptable.
OL,11,F"South West Water should never have
OL,12,Fallowed it to get to the state that
OL,13,Fit's currently in."
OL,15,FThe firm is providing tankered water
OL,16,Fto replenish supply missing from the
OL,17,Fsystem, which is between 5:30am and
OL,18,F10:30pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,F"Even then, customers tell me they
OL,7,Fstill aren't getting the supply due to
OL,8,Flow water pressure".
OL,10,FLast year, South West Water launched a
OL,11,Ffive-year #3.2 billion investment plan.
OL,13,FMr George said: "It's taken until now
OL,14,Ffor South West Water to realise they
OL,15,Fshould be investing money in the
OL,16,Fsystems which provide water and safe,
OL,17,Fclean sewage systems with a stronger
OL,18,Fsense of urgency than they have done
OL,19,Fpreviously".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,FSouth West Water has agreed to attend
OL,7,Fa meeting with the MP for St Ives in
OL,8,Fthe coming weeks.
OL,10,FA statement from the supplier reads:
OL,11,F"We're sorry for the disruption some
OL,12,Fcustomers in West Cornwall have
OL,13,Fexperienced and understand the impact.
OL,15,F"Increased seasonal demand is putting
OL,16,Fpressure on the network.
OL,18,F"We are currently carrying out
OL,19,Fupgrades to the Steeple service
OL,20,Freservoir, which we expect to be fully
OL,21,Foperational by the end of June.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780315873
OL,3,CCornwall businesses 'frustrated' by
OL,4,Cmonths of water supply issues
OL,6,F"In the meantime, we are putting
OL,7,Farrangements in place for tankering to
OL,8,Fhelp maintain supplies where needed.
OL,10,F"We'll continue to keep the community
OL,11,Fupdated as this work progresses."
OL,13,FThe company also said that customers
OL,14,Faffected for extended periods will be
OL,15,Fdue compensation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
